/docs/*
!/docs/blog/
/docs/blog/*
!/docs/blog/how-we-use-google-cloud-kms-to-verify-sleeksign-documents.md
/scripts/
PLATFORM_BUILD_BRIEF.md

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
